<h2><strong>What are the Major Trading Sessions?</strong></h2>
<p>The major trading sessions for EUR/USD currency pairs are London, New York, Tokyo, and Sydney.</p>
<h2>What are the Market Open and Close Times?</h2>
<p>The forex market opens at 9:00 PM GMT on Sunday and closes at 10:00 PM GMT on Friday. The first trading session to start is the Sydney session, and the last session to end is the New York session.</p>
